Description_lang: Imperator Mar'gok blasts a random player with Arcane energy, branding them for $156225d.When Branded expires it inflicts $156239s1 Arcane damage to the wearer and jumps to their closest ally within $156234A1 yards.Each time Arcane Wrath jumps, its damage increases by 25% and range decreases by 25%.Fortification: The jump range of Arcane Wrath is only decreased by 25% with each jump.
